Description: A rickety mattress with fluff and springs sticking out of it.
An empty bed panel. No mattress.
A shaky bunk with wooden legs.
A bed with an ornate canopy over the top.
A nice-looking king-sized bed.
Standard bed with a second bed on top it. If possible, allow 2 players to occupy the bed: one on-top and one below.
Standard bed. Nothing special. But not too shabby.
Clear but slightly blue-tinted shower cubicle. Rectangular. Door can be opened to enter the cubicle.
Wall poster depicting a long shot of MCC Island.
Poster with Noxite pointing outward similarly to old American recruiting propaganda.
Poster showing the art for Hole in the Wall.
Poster depicting the founding members of Noxcrew.
Poster with a gold cup depicted.
Poster with the MCC Zombie riding his chicken.
Freestanding sink.
A table lamp that can toggle on / off. Shade is conical in shape.
An N64-like gaming device with the Noxcrew logo on it.
A single sheet of paper.
Small collection of shirts, pants, and socks.
Wire cup full of various colors of pens.
Growing plant in a pot. Maybe some flowers.
Small plant in a clay pot.
Large, Rectangular Mirror
Fuzzy white mat placeable on the floor.
Potted plant suspended from rope.
Round vase with an opening in the top. Toggle puts flowers in it.
Standing lamp with a semicircular lampshade. Can be turned on / off.
A table lamp that can toggle on / off. Shade is rectangular in shape.
Ovular base taller than wide. Toggle puts flowers in it.
Empty wall rack meant for towels. Can place 1 item on it.

Wooden tub like this: https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&url=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.rhtubs.com%2Fteak-oval-tub-p%2F4x3x3tkoval.htm&psig=AOvVaw0Gll_olt0Y1RNDJvfsrfm2&ust=1624635725826000&source=images&cd=vfe&ved=0CAoQjRxqFwoTCLDZiu3NsPECFQAAAAAdAAAAABAD
Large, multi-armed fan. Toggles slow, fast, and off.
Chromatic keyboard and mouse with a nice PC. Can be toggled on to show Minecraft playing on the computer.
Large tv. When toggled, can be turned on, flip through several channels (animated gifs), and turned off.
Normal-looking vase. Toggle causes it to shatter into pieces or put itself back together.
Solid Gold toilet. Lid can be opened or closed.
Black woodstove with a chute. Can be opened, lit, closed, opened, and extinguished.
A grey-black clothing iron. When used, flips down and moves back and forth across its surface, briefly ironing it.
A clear jar filled with delicious-looking cookies. Toggle opens or closes the jar.
A desk fan. Can be toggled on / off. When on, it moves left-to-right.
Grey dishwasher. Can be toggled open / closed. When open, it reveals several plates and dishes inside.
A fancy-looking coat rack with ornate arms.
A dressing table with a full rectangular mirror for the player to look at themselves.
Chromatic and very nice-looking PC Tower.
Massive cordion of flowers and leaves hanging from ropes.
Large fan that stands upright on atall base. When toggled on, the fan moves left-to-right.
A monitor, keyboard, and mouse together. Old-fashioned and nothing special. Can be toggled on to show 'Pong' playing on the computer.
A pile of wood. Interacting with it sets it on fire (like a campfire).
Stone / Rock fireplace. Fire can be toggled on / off.
A pale green rotary phone. When used, the rotary winds up briefly.
Small tube TV. Can be toggled on / off. When on, displays static.
Medium white mashing machine. When toggled, it will rock back and forth as though it's turned on and full of clothes.
An analog clock with two bells. Interacting with the clock causes it to start or stop ringing.
Sink with two separate sections and drains.
Plain white toilet with the seat down. When activated, it opens and flushes.
Clear white bathtub.
A wooden coat rack.
Diamond-shaped table lamp that can toggle on / off. Shade is like a rhombus in shape.
White vase with a floral pattern. Toggle puts flowers in it.
Collection of leaves and vines suspended from rope.
Standard PC Tower. Nothing fancy, and a little old.
A plain white refrigerator. Can be opened and closed to reveal some food inside!
Lamp where rectangular paper stretches from bottom to top on all sides. Can be turned on / off.
Standing lamp with a fancy, conical lampshade. Can be turned on / off.
